sellItem_Label.text: PICK A PLACE TO SELL YOUR ITEM

welcomeText_CarBootBonus.text: PICK A CUSTOMER TO RECEIVE AN OFFER

paytable_1_text_12.text: ALL AWARDS ARE MULTIPLES OF LINE BET AND PAY FROM LEFT TO RIGHT.

paytable_1_text_13.text: ONLY THE HIGHEST WIN ON A PAYLINE IS PAID FOR THAT PAYLINE.

paytable_1_text_15.text: ACTS AS WILD AND SUBSTITUTES FOR

paytable_1_text_17.text: PAYS FROM LEFT TO RIGHT ONLY ON PAYLINES.

paytable_4_text_1.text: 3, 4 OR 5 BONUS SYMBOLS IN VIEW TRIGGER THE ATTIC BONUS.

paytable_4_text_2.text: PICK A HIGHLIGHTED ITEM FROM THE ATTIC.

paytable_4_text_3.text: CHOOSE TO SELL IT AT THE CARBOOT SALE OR AUCTION.

paytable_4_text_4.text: IN THE CAR BOOT SALE ONE OF FOUR CUSTOMER WILL MAKE AN OFFER FOR THE ITEM THAT CAN EITHER BE ACCEPTED OR REJECTED. IF REJECTED THE NEXT CUSTOMER WILL MAKE ANOTHER OFFER. THIS CARRIES ON UNTIL EITHER AN OFFER IS ACCEPTED OR THREE ARE REJECTED, IN WHICH CASE THE VALUE OF THE FOURTH OFFER WILL BE AWARDED.

paytable_4_text_5.text: AT THE AUCTION, BIDS INCREASE UNTIL THE ITEM IS SOLD.

paytable_4_text_6.text: THE ATTIC BONUS WIN IS THE VALUE THAT THE ITEM HAS BEEN SOLD FOR.

paytable_5_text_1.text: WHEN THE SAME SYMBOL (INCLUDING WILD SUBSTITUTIONS) APPEAR ON 3, 4 OR 5 CONSECUTIVE REELS

paytable_5_text_2.text: FROM LEFT TO RIGHT BUT ARE NOT ON A PAYLINE, THERE IS A CHANCE OF A WINDFALL BONUS AWARD. THE

paytable_5_text_3.text: AWARD IS FOR THE NUMBER OF CONSECUTIVE REELS AND DEFINED BY THE PAYTABLE BELOW

paytable_5_text_4.text: ALL AWARDS ARE MULTIPLES OF LINE BET

paytable_6_text_1.text: THE TOTAL STAKE IS SPLIT EQUALLY BETWEEN 20 PAYLINES TO GIVE THE LINE BET.

paytable_6_text_2.text: ALL AWARDS PAY FOR WINNING COMBINATIONS FROM LEFT TO RIGHT ON PAYLINES ONLY, EXCEPT WINDFALL BONUS AND ATTIC BONUS WINS.

paytable_6_text_3.text: ONLY THE HIGHEST WIN ON A PAYLINE IS PAID FOR THAT PAYLINES.

paytable_6_text_4.text: LINE WIN AWARDS AND WINDFALL BONUS WINS ARE EXPRESSED AS MULTIPLIERS OF LINE BET.

paytable_6_text_6.text: THE LONG TERM PAYBACK FOR THIS GAME IS 96.11%.

paytable_6_text_7.text: MALFUNCTION VOIDS ALL PAYS AND PLAYS.

paytable_7_text_1.text: ALL SINGLE ACTIVITY BUTTONS(E.G. 'CONTINUE', 'CLICK TO START', ETC.)CAN BE SELECTED BY PRESSING SPACE BAR OR ENTER KEY.

paytable_7_text_2.text: TO GO TO PAYTABLE DIRECTLY, PRESS 'I' KEY. TO NAVIGATE THE PAGES, USE LEFT RIGHT ARROW KEYS. PRESSING 'I' KEY AGAIN WILL EXIT THE PAYTABLE.

 게임을 다시 실행하고 다시 시도하세요.
